<div class="panel panel-warning">
	<div class="panel-heading">
		<h4 class="panel-title">
		<a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#accordion2_1">
		1. How to logout.? </a>
		</h4>
	</div>
	<div id="accordion2_1" class="panel-collapse collapse in">
		<div class="panel-body">
			<p>
				To logout, Please click the link indicated with your account name at the top right of the browser,
				The logout link will be shown, then click the logout link to logout. 
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="panel panel-success">
	<div class="panel-heading">
		<h4 class="panel-title">
		<a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#accordion2_1">
		1. How to update my Personal account including my personal info, avatar and password.? </a>
		</h4>
	</div>
	<div id="accordion2_1" class="panel-collapse collapse in">
		<div class="panel-body">
			<p>
				To update your account, Please click the link indicated with your account name at the top right of the browser
				and you can see the "My Profile" link. Click that and the account page will be loaded.

				You can find two tabs which are Overview and Account settings. Click the account settings tab. Then update your account.

			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>